name: COLDACT NEW Capsule 20
description: COLDACT CAPSULE is a combination of Phenylephrine and Chlorpheniramine which belongs to the group of medicines called Nasal decongestants and Antihistamines respectively.

name: JinCold Capsule 20
description: Zincold Tablet is a combination medicine that effectively relieves symptoms of common cold such as blocked nose, runny nose, watery eyes, sneezing, and congestion or stuffiness. It helps to loosen thick mucus, making it easier to cough out. This makes it easier for air to move in and out.

name: Himalaya Tulsi Syrup
description: Himalaya Tulasi Syrup helps suppress cough and aids the mobilization of mucus. It assists in calming and dilating the lung's airways providing relief.

name: Aayudh Syrup
description: It is made using a variety of natural herbs with antiviral and immunity boosting properties that makes it helpful in case of viral infections and to increase the body's immunity. It is beneficial in viral and bacterial infections, sore throat, cough and cold, flu, etc., with antioxidant and immunomodulatory properties.

name: Crocin tablet
description: It is used to reduce fever and treat mild to moderate pain. Also, it is used to relieve headache, migraine, toothache.

name: Cofsils
description: Cofsils cough syrup is a combination medicine containing diphenhydramine, ammonium chloride, and sodium citrate which helps in reducing cough.

name: Medformin Hydrochloride tablet
description: Metformin is used to treat high blood sugar levels that are caused by a type of diabetes mellitus or sugar diabetes called type 2 diabetes.

name: Sunrise Diabic Care Juice
description: Diabic Care Juice is beneficial in controlling all types of diabetes naturally, urinary disorder, frequent urination etc. Stimulate insulin secretion and helps in boosting immunity.

name: Easy Touch Control Solution
description: Glucose Monitoring system is working correctly and giving accurate results. The system is performing correctly if the control solution test result falls within the specific control solution range listed on your Test Strip vial.

name: G-Leuhr Diaboherb Liquid
description: Diaboherb Plus Oral Liquid is a natural herbal medicine that helps to stimulate the pancreatic cells to produce more insulin thereby controlling the blood sugar levels.

name: One Touch glucometer
description: Recognize the pattern of blood glucose levels (when the blood glucose levels are likely to become high or low).

name: Saridon

description: Headache Drops are effective for treating headache, migraine, mental stress, indigestion, nervousness, headache associated with nausea and vomiting.

name: Go-Mygraine tablets
description: It contains ashwagandha, which relieves migraines by soothing the nervous system and helps with stress and anxiety.
